div.p:
Then after ſome further diſcourſe, they ſhewed themſelves
to be willing to debate the buſineſſe concerning the high places;
whereupon the queſtion was ſtated.

And if by ſpirit you meane the directions of the ſpirit, its true;
and by the ſpirit may be meant the ſpirit of a man, as Paul ſaith,
whom I ſerve in my ſpirit.
